data.description: GREAT LOCATION! 4 Bedroom townhome in the highly desired High Point! Location is phenomenal! Lower level guest bed & full Bath! Primary Suite and 2 additional bedrooms on the 3rd floor! Large open living area in middle floor! Tile in all Baths & Laundry! Rear Entry 2-car Garage! Lots of upgrades throughout! Tree line backs to the rear. Must See! This home is protected by a 2-10 Home Warranty available for purchase at closing. If not purchased at closing, the warranty expires the date of closing.
